  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>One-Shot, One-Kill</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from 3 unique loadouts and 5 distinct weapons each with different play styles based on authentic airsoft weapons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make Every BB Count.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152530/extras/d78c37e9e31f652a5cf63798410e85af.poster.avif?t=1771525837\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152530/extras/d78c37e9e31f652a5cf63798410e85af.webm?t=1771525837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152530/extras/d78c37e9e31f652a5cf63798410e85af.mp4?t=1771525837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Team Deathmatch, Domination or Free-For-All Battles Alongside Your Friends. </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Host your own games or simply join an existing game— the choice is yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152530/extras/65d866ddb812111f70db65a7d72a9335.poster.avif?t=1771525837\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152530/extras/65d866ddb812111f70db65a7d72a9335.webm?t=1771525837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152530/extras/65d866ddb812111f70db65a7d72a9335.mp4?t=1771525837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fast Paced Gameplay</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Small maps with fast respawn times mean the action is always just around the corner.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152530/extras/6cafe399ec9cb5c60582026c355e51ec.poster.avif?t=1771525837\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152530/extras/6cafe399ec9cb5c60582026c355e51ec.webm?t=1771525837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152530/extras/6cafe399ec9cb5c60582026c355e51ec.mp4?t=1771525837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
